RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.contract_ref_no FROM tltbs_contract_master a ,oltbs_contract b where a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no and a.version_no = b.latest_version_no and b.contract_status = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM smvws_user_branches c WHERE c.Branch_code = a.branch and c.User_id = global.USER_ID)
SELECT b.customer_no , b.customer_name1 FROM lbtbs_part_proc_stat a , oltms_customer b where a.borrower_ref_no = ? and a.counterparty = b.customer_no
SELECT a.customer_no ,a.customer_name1 FROM oltms_customer a WHERE record_stat = 'O' AND auth_stat = 'A'
